column1: It's time to get physical, folks! Get ready to flex those muscles and push your limits in the ultimate wrestling showdown. Feel the intensity as bodies collide and voices grunt with effort. Singlets stretched to their limits, who will emerge victorious in this no-holds-barred battle? Time to find out, 3...2...1...LET'S WRESTLE!

Attention all boot campers! It's time to gear up and get ready for an epic night of fun and adventure. Break out your sluttiest camo and shine up those dog tags, because we're about to go hard! And don't worry about getting bored - we've got a top-notch DJ and some seriously sexy guys to keep you entertained all night long. So let's get pumped and show everyone what we're made of! Boot camp is about to commence - are you ready to rise to the challenge?

column1: On June 4th, 2023, BOS Philly is taking over the Muses Stage at the Philadelphia Pride Festival, right in the heart of the Gayborhood!
Join us on Locust Street, between Juniper and 13th Street, as we take over the stage from 1pm to 4:30pm with the HOTTEST beats and COOLEST DJs from our amazing community!
At 1pm, prepare to be mesmerized by Riva and Bianca from Solar Sounds as they kick-start the ultimate celebration!
At 2:30pm, let the electrifying sounds of DJ K!RK take you on a wild ride with the best circuit music this city has ever experienced!

We plan to pack the streets with non-stop energy and the most unforgettable dance party EVER! You seriously don't want to miss this! Come and make some memories with us and dance the day away under the sun as we celebrate PRIDE, love, and unity!
Don't forget to spread the word and let's make Philly Pride 2023 the most talked-about event of the year!

Unleash your inner glow and dive into BOS Philly's Annual Black Light Party!  Prepare to be mesmerized as your glowing underwear and hypnotic body paint light up the dance floor like never before!  Feel the beats of Miami's DJ Jace M!  Don't miss out where YOU are invited to shine!

Join us at the BIKE STOP‍ for SUMMER CAMP. Gear up and let's take a GAY-cation back to the time when life was all about pitching tents and salivating over that HOT camp counselor! BOS Philly is here to remind you what RAGING in the woods was all about! So hike up those booty shorts, tighten that tank top, and strut your stuff. The camp-bell has rung, and we're ready to PLAY! If you're a GOOD little camper, you just earn a merit badge
Enjoy the summer with our incredible White Party. Pick your favorite all white outfit, or just a hot white jock strap for a night of music and fun at the Bike Stop

Saddle up and get ready for the most rootin'-tootin', fabulous, and flamboyant event this side of the Mississippi - The Wild West Party! Put on your best cowboy boots and fringed chaps, but don't forget to add that glitter and sparkle. You're in for a wild night! Yippee-Ki-Yay, Motherfucker

Get ready to jingle those bells and deck the halls, because Nut Cracker, the naughtiest and most fabulous Christmas-themed party is coming to town! With festive cheer and queer vibes aplenty, this once-a-year extravaganza is where you'll want to spend your holiday nights!

Nut Cracker is the titillating gift that keeps on giving! So slip into your naughtiest holiday outfits, and join us for the merriest, most glamorous party of the season! This will be one unforgettable night where you'll be begging Santa to put you on his naughty list

Join us for the spine-chilling Halloween party where terror meets fabulousness! Dare to delve into the darkest corners of your imagination, and unleash your most horrifying and creative costumes that will haunt the dance floor. Get ready for a night full of monstrous entertainment, petrifying performances, and thrilling tunes spun by our fiendishly fabulous DJ. Unleash your inner creature of the night. Dig out your cobwebs, don your menacing masks, and cast your bewitching spells – it's time to raise the spirits at the most ghoulishly glam affair of the season. The ultimate Halloween party that will leave you screaming for more!
Get ready to unleash your wild side

Welcome to our sultry and seductive jungle oasis, where inhibitions are left at the door, and the untamed reign free. Join us and be a part of the sexiest tribe on the planet, as the hottest DJ from around the world sends shockwaves through your body with heart-pounding beats that will make you dance the night away.

Slither into your sexiest jungle-themed attire, and let your inhibitions run wild as you become one with nature. Flex those toned muscles as Tarzan, or channel your inner animal with a fierce leopard print ensemble. Anything goes in this untamed land, so come ready to show off your wild side!

Welcome to the Jungle. Embrace your inner beast, and let the spirit of the wild take over. Your adventure begins now!

Opening: DJ Jace M
